snippet.title: Space Crusade gameplay (PC Game, 1992)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Space Crusade, Dos PC game produced by Gremlin Interactive in 1992 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/space-crusade/680/
I played through the first mission as the Blood Angels, blowing away orks and gretchin.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Star Rangers - https://youtu.be/IsvaGESf_jg
Wetlands - https://youtu.be/HuZUNqql-p4
Darklight Conflict - https://youtu.be/sDmdeLoGlVg
